      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of opportunity, this vehicle offers dependable transportation at an accessible price point. An excellent choice for a value-focused buyer, first-time driver, or anyone seeking a practical project, it delivers straightforward ownership with room to make it your own. Priced to sell and presented with honest value, this is a smart way to get on the road without overspending.",
