    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with a lot of life experience and plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great chance for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a handy runaround without spending big. It has the kind of honest character you expect from a well-used vehicle, and it\u2019s being offered as a straightforward, budget-friendly buy. If you appreciate a no-nonsense deal and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a really worthwhile pick-up.",
      "price": 5900.0,
