      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for someone who wants an inexpensive driver or weekend project. This car shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but it still has a lot going for it: the engine pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels composed. A practical platform with good bones, straightforward mechanicals, and plenty of upside for an owner willing to sort the smaller details. If you want affordable entry-level transportation with potential, this one is worth a look.",
